	"content": "<h1 class=\"page-title\">Assigned Readings and Schedule</h1>\n  \n  <div id=\"todo-date-mount-point\"></div>\n  \n    <p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Note: </span>the due dates for the below assigned readings will be announced as we move through the semester.</p>\n<p><strong>I.A Introduction</strong>: 8/25-9/8</p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n<ul>\n<li>Mingst: skim Chapters 1, 2, 4, and 5. The expectation for this lengthy reading assignment is to simply become familiar with the topics.</li>\n<li>Discuss with the TA: <span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a class=\"file_preview_link previewable\" title=\"Ra'anan.pdf\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/124722/files/80031140/download?wrap=1\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/124722/files/80031140\" data-api-returntype=\"File\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"preview_1\">Ra’anan “The Nation-State Fallacy”</a><a class=\"file_download_btn\" role=\"button\" download=\"\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/124722/files/80031140/download?download_frd=1\"><span role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"m1807.093 1482.477 79.736 79.963-355.313 355.312H355.346L.035 1562.44l79.85-79.963 322.22 322.334H1484.76l322.334-322.334ZM997.677-.033v1167.02l355.313-355.313 79.962 79.85-491.858 491.633L449.46 891.524l79.962-79.85 355.313 355.313V-.033h112.941Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><span class=\"screenreader-only\">Download Ra’anan “The Nation-State Fallacy”</span></a><div role=\"region\" class=\"preview_container\" id=\"preview_1\" style=\"display: none;\"></div></span></li>\n<li>Discuss with the TA: <span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\">